Britney Spears, 40, wowed fans on social media as she shared a new post featuring herself taking a dip in the ocean while topless. The Toxic singer took to Instagram today to upload an insight into her exotic beach holidays with her 40 million followers. The picture showed the pop star swimming away from the camera in the turquoise waters, with her derriere visible above the water. She could be seen wearing nothing but a yellow thong bikini bottom during her getaway to Maui. The Grammy Award-winner captioned the shot: “Say hello to my booty.” Britney’s post sparked a barrage of comments from fans, who were doing exactly what she suggested in the caption. One user also pointed out the blonde beauty’s “amazing” back muscles, while another branded her “iconic”.